name: People #2
description:
I believe that the eyes are the only elements showing the whole soul and the story of humans.
-
It has been about 15 years since I started painting. In the past 10 years, I’ve conducted a personal project that
contains a series of portraits.
In these paintings I have captured the essence of particular moments or a gaze of a person that has impressed me at first glance.
Size:4000px-3500px
